{"comments":"Tooltip Choreography — Entrance, exit, and follow animations.\n\n## Overview\n\nTooltips don't just \"appear\" — they're choreographed to create spatial\ncontinuity and guide the user's attention. This module defines the\ncomplete animation lifecycle for tour tooltips.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\n- Entry: Tooltip slides in from the direction of its arrow\n- Exit: Tooltip anticipates the next target's direction\n- Follow: Tooltip smoothly tracks scrolling targets\n- Micro-interactions: Buttons respond to hover and focus\n\nEach preset is tuned for different contexts:\n- Default: Balanced for most use cases\n- Minimal: Fast, for reduced motion or power users\n- Dramatic: Attention-grabbing for onboarding\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Complete choreography configuration for tooltip animations.\n\nControls every aspect of tooltip animation lifecycle.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["entryDuration",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["exitDuration",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["entryDelay",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["entrySpring",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Tour","Motion","Spring"],"SpringParams"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["exitSpring",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Tour","Motion","Spring"],"SpringParams"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["entryDistance",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["scaleFrom",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":